fields.description:
Hey guys,

I imported the kitchen sink in an attempt to continue learning app development, but it absolutely won't run on Android for me. I tried directly off of my Galaxy Tab 10.1 but the same thing happens.

The log file doesn't display much either...

comments.body:
It appears to be a configuration issue. I would appreciate if you can attach your build.log file to diagnose this issue further. Please run the following command and attach the output:

titanium info

Marking this as "Cannot reproduce". Please provide us necessary info requested in this ticket so that we can help you. If we don't hear back from you in a week, we will assume this issue is resolved and the ticket can be closed.
